  "instructions": [
    "In a pressure cooker, melt the butter over medium-high heat. Add the onion and garlic and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the jalapeños and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the shrimp and cook until pink, about 2 minutes per side.",
    "Add the flour and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Gradually add the heavy cream, whisking constantly.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 2 minutes or until thickened.",
    "Stir in the cinnamon and sugar.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Serve the dish hot, garnished with chopped cilantro."
